OL,5, Two airline passengers accused of      
OL,6, "unruly behaviour" have been hit with  
OL,7, the largest fines ever proposed by the 
OL,8, US Federal Aviation Administration.    
OL,10,FThe five-figure penalties on the two   
OL,11,Fflyers accused of violence are part of 
OL,12,F$2m (#1.5m) in fines levied this year. 
OL,14,FUS airlines have seen record numbers of
OL,15,Fdisruptive passengers since early 2021,
OL,16,Fwith many incidents involving the      
OL,17,Frefusal to wear an anti-viral facemask.
OL,19,FThe fines were announced by transport  
OL,20,Fsecretary Pete Buttigieg on Friday.    
